To use this program, type "python expose.py spec-file" at the command line.

GCCXML is assumed to be installed and in the path. Get the CVS version by
following the directions at http://www.gccxml.org/HTML/Download.html

The specification file specifies what interface to expose to python. It is an
XML file described by expose.xsd (not verified). See "test/test_compile.py" for
a very basic example. More documentation will be added later.
